WEBVTT

00:02.240 --> 00:04.550
[♪♪♪]

00:04.760 --> 00:07.639
ANNOUNCER:
<i>This is the story of two sisters:</i>

00:08.080 --> 00:11.630
<i>Jessica Tate and Mary Campbell.</i>

00:11.840 --> 00:15.914
<i>Jessica lives in a neighbourhood</i>
<i>known as rich.</i>

00:16.320 --> 00:17.879
<i>Jessica likes life.</i>

00:18.080 --> 00:20.993
<i>The only thing about life</i>
<i>she would change, if she could,</i>

00:21.200 --> 00:23.760
<i>is that she would</i>
<i>set it all to music.</i>

00:25.000 --> 00:28.516
<i>The Tates have more secrets</i>
<i>than they do money.</i>

00:31.360 --> 00:34.558
<i>We're approaching</i>
<i>Mary Campbell's house.</i>

00:36.360 --> 00:37.919
<i>Mary, too, likes life.</i>

00:38.120 --> 00:41.955
<i>Unfortunately, life doesn't seem</i>
<i>to be too crazy about her.</i>

00:42.160 --> 00:46.951
<i>As you can see, the Campbells</i>
<i>don't have nearly as much money</i>
<i>as the Tates.</i>

00:47.600 --> 00:51.435
<i>They do, however,</i>
<i>have as many secrets.</i>

00:55.280 --> 00:57.237
<i>In last week's episode of</i> Soap,

00:57.440 --> 01:00.239
<i>Jessica convinced herself</i>
<i>that Chester's infidelity,</i>

01:00.440 --> 01:03.512
<i>and all the bad things that have</i>
<i>befallen the Tates and the Campbells,</i>

01:03.720 --> 01:05.757
<i>are a result of a curse.</i>

01:05.960 --> 01:09.795
<i>But even though they're cursed,</i>
<i>she's still not too thrilled with Chester.</i>

01:10.080 --> 01:12.595
<i>The Godfather</i>
<i>came looking for Danny,</i>

01:12.800 --> 01:14.439
<i>but Danny was dressed as a rabbi.</i>

01:14.640 --> 01:16.472
<i>And instead of getting killed,</i>

01:16.680 --> 01:18.114
<i>Danny got a contribution.</i>

01:18.360 --> 01:21.990
<i>Burt, who came away from Dr. Medlow</i>
<i>thinking he could, couldn't,</i>

01:22.200 --> 01:25.557
<i>because Mary,</i>
<i>upset over the day's events, wouldn't.</i>

01:25.800 --> 01:29.430
<i>Dennis told Jodie there was no need</i>
<i>for a sex-change operation</i>

01:29.640 --> 01:32.633
<i>because he's decided</i>
<i>to marry a girl.</i>

01:32.840 --> 01:35.992
<i>On hearing the news, Jodie swallowed</i>
<i>the contents of the pill cart</i>

01:36.200 --> 01:39.318
<i>for the entire west wing</i>
<i>of University Hospital.</i>

01:39.600 --> 01:44.470
<i>Confused? You won't be</i>
<i>after this week's episode of</i> Soap.

